<p><strong>4. 49% of marketers identify organic search as the top ROI-driving channel.</strong>
(Source: <a href="https://genesysgrowth.com/blog/content-marketing-roi-stats-for-marketing-leaders">Genesys Growth</a>, 2026)
Organic search beats paid ads, social media, and email marketing as the highest-ROI channel in marketer surveys.</p>
<p><strong>5. 88% of marketers maintain or increase SEO budgets year-over-year.</strong>
(Source: SeoProfy, 2026)
