<p><strong>6. 60% of marketers say inbound strategies like SEO generate the highest-quality leads.</strong>
(Source: HubSpot, 2025)
Lead quality matters more than lead volume. SEO attracts buyers with purchase intent. Paid ads attract browsers.</p>
<p><strong>7. Organic search drives 53.3% of all website traffic.</strong>
